{"id": 1890, "genre": 1000, "title": "你对访谈类的节目有哪些不满？", "description": "你如何定义“好好聊天”？你从访谈里如何收获新知？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 11215, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201709051117290hvNmswWdlMKAczF.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-06T17:00:57Z", "questions": [{"id": 2919, "title": "你对访谈类的节目有哪些不满？", "content": "你对访谈类的节目有哪些不满？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 233785, "content": "主持人存在感弱，完全以听故事小孩的样子看嘉宾自吹自擂", "image": "img/option/option/20170905134521Kzrc0jd8UPWna1OH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233786, "content": "煽情升华病，不管说的啥内容，最后一定要归纳总结、拔高主题", "image": "img/option/option/20170905141717FIBd87tewNmAJVqY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233819, "content": "主持方或者嘉宾不做功课，常识性错误乱入，鸡同鸭讲", "image": "img/option/option/20170905141833uvmqkQjUf9y4ETW6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233820, "content": "千篇一律，看同一个公众人物在不同节目上把同样的话说很多遍", "image": "img/option/option/20170905142024UVC7J9RMvQX4nPdb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233821, "content": "主持人执着于表达自己观点，请嘉宾也是为了证明“我是对的，是吧！”", "image": "img/option/option/201709051421388bcBhQdUmSMvHg4N.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233822, "content": "主持人和嘉宾没有实质对话，本质上是各说各的", "image": "img/option/option/20170905143132TMBGI1pV3RxfhwZs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233823, "content": "嘉宾没有内涵，本质上属于“无话可说”，只能卖人设表演", "image": "img/option/option/20170905143557TPaolOJ8EtN51X7R.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233824, "content": "努力“接地气”做关于普通人的节目，结果没主线没看头", "image": "img/option/option/20170905143633saf60gBKmQ7oeUvS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}